+
+| Estado | Cantidad |
+| --- | ---: |
+| PASS | 0 |
+| FAIL | 0 |
+| BLOQUEADO | 0 |
+| NO_APLICA | 0 |
+| PENDIENTE_MANUAL | 28 |
+
